{"title":"idea下配置vim模式","uid":"9b2c63c47c8da4d4585e94b67802d226","slug":"intellij-idea-config-vim","date":"2023-09-22T17:04:46.000Z","updated":"2023-09-22T09:41:55.261Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/intellij-idea-config-vim.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://source.unsplash.com/1200x628","content":"<!--toc:start-->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#vim%E6%90%93%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87\">vim搓一切?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">安装</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEideavimrc\">配置<code>.ideavimrc</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%AE%A9%E5%85%B6%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88\">让其生效</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#FBI-WARNING\">FBI WARNING</a><!--toc:end--></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"vim搓一切\"><a href=\"#vim搓一切\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vim搓一切?\"></a>vim搓一切?</h1><p>有一说一,vim虽然可以配置的很舒服,但是对于<code>java</code>程序员来说,用vim去写<code>java</code>是真的折磨,除非你想进行自我折磨,变成代码仙人.<br>所以最省心的方案就是在<code>idea</code>中下一个vim插件</p>\n<h1 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h1><p>首先你要有一个java第一个IDE:<code>intellij idea</code><br>然后打开插件市场,下一个idea vimrc 安装上</p>\n<h1 id=\"配置-ideavimrc\"><a href=\"#配置-ideavimrc\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置.ideavimrc\"></a>配置<code>.ideavimrc</code></h1><p>创建一个<code>~/.ideavimrc</code></p>\n<p>加入一些配置:</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki dracula\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                   ____       _      ____    ___    ____</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">                  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">__</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> )     / </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">\\ </span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">   / ___</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">_</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">_</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">/</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">___</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                  |  _ \\    / _ \\   \\___ \\   | |  | |</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">                  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">_</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">) </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">/</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">___</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">\\ </span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">___</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">) </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">___</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                  |____/  /_/   \\_\\ |____/  |___|  \\____|</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">basic</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">config</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">!--swig￼0-</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">-</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                   ____    _       _   _    ____   ___   _   _</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">                  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">_</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">\\ </span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">     </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">/</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">___</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">_</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">_</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                  | |_) | | |     | | | | | |  _   | |  |  \\| |</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">                  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">__/</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">___</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">_</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">_</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                  |_|     |_____|  \\___/   \\____| |___| |_| \\_|</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">plugin</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">config</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">!--swig￼1-</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">-</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">&#125;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">Plug</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E9F284\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">tpope/vim-surround</span><span style=\"color: #E9F284\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;USAGE &#123;&#123;&#123;&#123;\n\" [count][\"x]gr&#123;motion&#125;   Replace &#123;motion&#125; text with the contents of register x.\n\"                         Especially when using the unnamed register, this is\n\"                         quicker than \"_d&#123;motion&#125;P or \"_c&#123;motion&#125;<C-R>\"\n\" [count][\"x]grr          Replace [count] lines with the contents of register x.\n\"                         To replace from the cursor position to the end of the\n\"                         line use [\"x]gr$\n\" &#123;Visual&#125;[\"x]gr          Replace the selection with the contents of register x.\"\n\"&#125;&#125;&#125;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">Plug &#39;vim-scripts/ReplaceWithRegister&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">USAGE</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">!--swig￼3-</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">-</span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">&#125;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">Plug</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E9F284\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">tommcdo/vim-exchange</span><span style=\"color: #E9F284\">&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">Plug</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E9F284\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">terryma/vim-multiple-cursors</span><span style=\"color: #E9F284\">&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot; quick-scop cofnig</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">let g:qs_highlight_on_keys = [&#39;f&#39;, &#39;F&#39;, &#39;t&#39;, &#39;T&#39;]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">let g:qs_accepted_chars = [&#39;a&#39;, &#39;b&#39;, &#39;c&#39;, &#39;d&#39;, &#39;e&#39;, &#39;f&#39;, &#39;g&#39;, &#39;h&#39;, &#39;i&#39;, &#39;j&#39;, &#39;k&#39;, &#39;l&#39;, &#39;m&#39;, &#39;n&#39;, &#39;o&#39;, &#39;p&#39;, &#39;q&#39;, &#39;r&#39;, &#39;s&#39;, &#39;t&#39;, &#39;u&#39;, &#39;v&#39;, &#39;w&#39;, &#39;x&#39;, &#39;y&#39;, &#39;z&#39;] </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">https://github.com/JetBrains/ideavim/wiki/ideajoin-examples</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #8BE9FD\">set</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">ideajoin</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #8BE9FD\">set</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">sneak</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;&#125;&#125;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">                   </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">_</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">__</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">_____</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">__</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">   </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">__</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">__</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">  </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">__</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">      </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">_</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">      </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">____</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                  | |/ / | ____| \\ \\ / / |  \\/  |    / \\    |  _ </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">\\</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\">                  </span><span style=\"color: #FF79C6\">|</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&#39; /  |  _|    \\ V /  | |\\/| |   / _ \\   | |_) |</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                  | . \\  | |___    | |   | |  | |  / ___ \\  |  __/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot;                  |_|\\_\\ |_____|   |_|   |_|  |_| /_/   \\_\\ |_|</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot; basic key map &#123;&#123;&#123;inoremap <C-e> <END>\ninoremap <C-a> <HOME>\ninoremap <C-f> <Right>\ninoremap <C-b> <Left>\ninoremap <C-n> <Down>\ninoremap <C-p> <Up>\ninoremap <M-f> <S-Right>\ninoremap <M-b> <S-Left>\ninoremap <C-k> <ESC>d$i\ninoremap <C-d> <Del>\n\n\nlet mapleader=\" \"\n\"&#125;&#125;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot; idea action config &#123;&#123;&#123;\nnnoremap gd <Action>(GotoDeclaration)\nnnoremap gi <Action>(GotoImplementation)\nnnoremap gs <Action>(GotoSuperMethod)\nnnoremap gt <Action>(GotoTypeDeclaration)\n\nmap <leader>re  <Action>(RenameElement)\n\nmap <leader>gf <Action>(GotoFile)\nmap <leader>gt <Action>(GotoSymbol)\n\n\nmap <leader>f: <Action>(GotoAction)\nmap <leader>f. <Action>(FindInPath)\nmap <leader>fl <Action>(RecentLocations)\nmap <leader>ff  <Action>(RecentFiles)\n\n\nmap <leader>et :NERDTreeToggle<CR>\nmap <leader>ef :NERDTreeFocus<CR>\nmap <leader>es <Action>(FileStructurePopup)\n\n\nnmap <C-W>q <Action>(CloseAllEditors)\n\"&#125;&#125;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #50FA7B\">&quot; plugin config &#123;&#123;&#123;\n\nlet g:multi_cursor_use_default_mapping=0\n\n\" Default mapping\nlet g:multi_cursor_start_word_key      = '<C-n>'\nlet g:multi_cursor_select_all_word_key = '<A-n>'\nlet g:multi_cursor_start_key           = 'g<C-n>'\nlet g:multi_cursor_select_all_key      = 'g<A-n>'\nlet g:multi_cursor_next_key            = '<C-n>'\nlet g:multi_cursor_prev_key            = '<C-p>'\nlet g:multi_cursor_skip_key            = '<C-x>'\nlet g:multi_cursor_quit_key            = '<Esc>'\n\" nmap <C-n> <Plug>NextWholeOccurrence\n\" xmap <C-n> <Plug>NextWholeOccurrence\n\" nmap g<C-n> <Plug>NextOccurrence\n\" xmap g<C-n> <Plug>NextOccurrence\n\" nmap <C-x> <Plug>SkipOccurrence\n\" xmap <C-x> <Plug>SkipOccurrence\n\" nmap <C-p> <Plug>RemoveOccurrence\n\" xmap <C-p> <Plug>RemoveOccurrence\n\" nmap <S-C-n> <Plug>AllWholeOccurrences\n\" xmap <S-C-n> <Plug>AllWholeOccurrences\n\" nmap g<S-C-n> <Plug>AllOccurrences\n\" xmap g<S-C-n> <Plug>AllOccurrences\n\n\"\"&#125;&#125;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><h1 id=\"让其生效\"><a href=\"#让其生效\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"让其生效\"></a>让其生效</h1><p>打开idea,source一下</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki dracula\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #8BE9FD\">source</span><span style=\"color: #F8F8F2\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F1FA8C\">~/.ideavimrc</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id=\"FBI-WARNING\"><a href=\"#FBI-WARNING\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"FBI WARNING\"></a>FBI WARNING</h1><ol>\n<li><code>.ideavimrc</code>里面有一些插件是要在idea中也要下载对应的插件才能使用的,具体参考<a href=\"https://github.com/JetBrains/ideavim/wiki/IdeaVim-Plugins\">这里</a></li>\n<li><code>map &lt;leader&gt;f: &lt;Action&gt;(GotoAction)</code> 这种形式是在调用<code>idea</code>的原生功能,具体有哪些功能,可以参考<a href=\"https://github.com/JetBrains/ideavim\">这里</a>,可以打开<code>ideavim</code>的插件,查看对应操作的<code>&lt;ActionId&gt;</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/post/intellij-idea-config-vim/track_action_dark.gif\" alt=\"track_action_id\"></p>\n","text":"如何在idea中配置vim,让写代码更加舒服...","permalink":"/post/intellij-idea-config-vim","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.5k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"idea","slug":"idea","count":1,"path":"api/categories/idea.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"idea","slug":"idea","count":1,"path":"api/tags/idea.json"},{"name":"vim","slug":"vim","count":2,"path":"api/tags/vim.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vim%E6%90%93%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vim搓一切?</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-ideavimrc\"><span class=\"toc-text\">配置.ideavimrc</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%A9%E5%85%B6%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\"